Instaling pycudd:

- Download pycudd from the website (http://bears.ece.ucsb.edu/pycudd.html)
- Apply the patch pycudd.patch
- cd cudd; ./setup.sh; make -f Makefile_64 libso
  This will end with errors but now there should be files in lib/ :
    libcuddepd.so
    libcuddmtr.so
    libcudd.so
    libcuddst.so
    libcuddutil.so
    libdddmp.so
- cd ../pycudd; make
- Add the library to the PYTHONPATH or install it locally

pycudd.py and _pycudd.so should now be available
